requirements FLTK lib:

sudo apt-get install libfltk1.3-dev
sudo apt-get install libx11-dev
sudo apt-get install libxinerama-dev
sudo apt-get install libxft-dev



compile command:

g++ `fltk-config --cxxflags` filename.cpp `fltk-config --libs` -lX11 -ldl -lXext -lXinerama -lXft -lfontconfig -o out_file_name

